Python<pre><code>scaleFanSpeed(raw_val: Any) -&gt; int
</code></pre> <p>Scales proprietary 0-15 fan speed values to a 0-100 percentage.</p> Source code in <code>src/bpm/bambutools.py</code> Python<pre><code>@staticmethod
def scaleFanSpeed(raw_val: Any) -&gt; int:
    """
    Scales proprietary 0-15 fan speed values to a 0-100 percentage.
    """
    try:
        val = int(raw_val)
        return min(max(round((val / 15.0) * 100), 0), 100)
    except Exception:
        return 0
</code></pre>

Python<pre><code>sortFileTreeAlphabetically(source) -&gt; dict
</code></pre> <p>Sorts a dict of file/directory nodes hierarchically.</p> Source code in <code>src/bpm/bambutools.py</code> Python<pre><code>@staticmethod
def sortFileTreeAlphabetically(source) -&gt; dict:
    """
    Sorts a dict of file/directory nodes hierarchically.
    """

    def sort_node_list(node_list):
        for item in node_list:
            if item.get("id", "").endswith("/") and "children" in item:
                item["children"] = sort_node_list(item["children"])
        return sorted(
            node_list,
            key=lambda i: (not i.get("id", "").endswith("/"), i.get("name", "").lower()),
        )

    source["children"] = sort_node_list(source["children"])
    return source
